{"tid":2375414,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"港大 Mecon 獨有 4 個 stream！可能係全世界最精心設計嘅 programme","createTime":"2021-01-22T04:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T04:59:39.000Z","uid":36383,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c4bb2561caea5b37968878345ecd8ea8e96b1f","tid":2375414,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FnMkhsX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFnMkhsX.jpg&h=48342af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先講 <span class=\"large\"><span class=\"violet\"><strong>data analysis stream:</strong></span></span> financial econometrics + causal inference + forecasting + computational and analysis of economic data 。簡直無敵可以讀完直接同各大 mstat/cs 去搶飯碗，讀得好分分鐘可以去搞 machine learning ，雖然唔知用 STATA/Excel 可以點做 analysis ，但真係好似好勁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再講 <span class=\"large\"><span class=\"pink\"><strong>policy analysis stream</strong></span></span>。又 Policy analysis 又 International econ，完全係為成為各大銀行經濟師鋪路，量產<del>末日博士</del>，可以發表評論大力抨擊美國財政及貨幣政策，將國際資金由香港引去新加坡 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後兩個 stream 係 <span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"teal\">theory / advanced econ stream</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 竟然見到有 econometrics theory 2 但 data analysis 個 stream 係冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個設計真係神奇，而且見到有 Research topics 呀 Research thesis 呀，真係為 PhD 鋪路，雖然讀完唔知有咩工好做"},{"pid":"7093f2c526f2447a5c44a6e40a28106e52acaf5d","tid":2375414,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"reply